    "In order to ask an LLM whether something is ethically problematic, one has to already have a suspicion that there may be a problem, or must ask specifically for every situation where there might be an ethical dilemma.",
    "However, awareness is connected to taking responsibility, which in turn connects to one's knowledge.",
    "As one group used ChatGPT to increase their knowledge of the case (e.g., why are international conferences held in remote places sometimes?",
    "), this could be an advantage of using LLMs in ethics education.",
    "Unfortunately, ChatGPT gave partially incorrect answers, which the students -not so familiar with the academic world -interpreted as completely correct."
  ],
